data.description: If you've been looking for a beautiful 5 bedroom home with a Mt Rainier view, look no further! This home has been beautifully and thoughtfully updated with new paint, flooring, ceiling fans, modern light fixtures - you name it! Fantastic large deck with Mt Rainier view is perfect for entertaining, BBQ's or relaxing in the evenings. The backyard is HUGE and offers a charming gazebo and endless space to garden, play and entertain plus there are no neighbors behind you making your backyard peaceful. Downstairs offers a living rm/flex space, 2 bedrooms, 1/2 bath and updated laundry rm. This home offers the best of both worlds: large property w/ easy commute to Oly & JBLM! Back on market, buyers got cold feet, no inspection performed
